text: Ordered the DIY steak and the spicy chicken breast bowls, overall tasted pretty yummy but weren’t very filling. Steak pairs really well with onsen egg!

Could be better.. portion was not as generous compare to other brands..

Ingredients could taste it’s kept frozen for awhile

Price is on the higher side compared to other salad bowl brands..

Tried the chicken and the duck (they were equally salty). The rest of the ingredients were good, the variety was excellent, and I've especially enjoyed their roasted garlic. The aircon was extremely noisy, so it wasn't a comfortable place to hang out.
ordered the trimmed ribeye steak and spicy chicken breast. overall tasted yummy and delicious, really liked the juicy-ness and tenderness of the steak.
I've always liked coming here for food. The food always tastes delicious but the price. The price is brutal! Honestly, if it is priced better, I would give it 5 stars!
